summary: This document details the consent to search provided by Alfredo Rodriguez on November 4, 2009. During the search of his vehicle, a tan Chevrolet Trailblazer, two cellular telephones were seized, including an AT&T Sony Ericsson and an iPhone. The consent form signed by Rodriguez was included in the case file.
